    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tools having a stretched wire used as a cutting edge, or trowel-like tools with a central slitlike blade, used to slice cheese.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
